snippet.title: Guild Wars 2: Heart of Thorns Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the official launch trailer for Guild Wars 2: Heart of Thorns, the first expansion of Guild Wars 2 coming on October 23! You can prepurchase Guild Wars 2: Heart of Thorns here: https://buy.guildwars2.com?cid=90:5::::NA:18:::

Subscribe to the Guild Wars 2 channel on YouTube for weekly developer videos, release videos and more! http://www.youtube.com/guildwars2

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/GuildWars2
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GuildWars2
Google+: https://plus.google.com/+guildwars2/
Tumblr: http://guildwars2.tumblr.com/
